dc_description_s: Hydrographic chart of the Fijian Islands showing towns and geographical features; In lower left margin: "Small corrections II.84, IX.84, ... 1918-835."; Relief shown by hachures and spot height. Depth shown by bathymetric soundings.; Oriented with north slightly to the right.; "From the surveys of Captain H.M. Denham, R.N.; F.R.S. 1854-6. Lieutenants W.U. Moore and G.E. Richards, R.N. 1876-82 with additions from the works of Commander C. Wilkes, U.S.N. and various other authorities."; "2691"--lower right.|63 x 96 centimeters|Scale approximately 1:740,000|General Map Collection
